sense.name: investigate or study methodically in great detail
sense.examples: We will analyse two Shakespearian sonnets tomorrow. Researchers analysed the purchases of 6300 households. Water samples taken from streams were analysed for contamination by chemicals. My job is to analyse today's financial market.

sense.name: psychoanalyze
sense.examples: Chris analysed me today. It was a little weird, cuz he was dead on. Dr. John Nash was analysed as schizophernic at 31 years of age.
